title: Correction to: Novel gurmarin-like peptides from Gymnema sylvestre and their interactions with the sweet taste receptor T1R2/T1R3
content: This is a correction to: Halim Maaroufi, Novel gurmarin-like peptides from Gymnema sylvestre and their interactions with the sweet taste receptor T1R2/T1R3, Chemical Senses, Volume 49, 2024, https://doi.org/10.1093/chemse/bjae018
